{"tid":1881022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家好，我係一個黎自平行時空嘅手足（短文）","createTime":"2020-02-15T09:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T11:56:04.000Z","uid":323043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02ab2acc959de60a724c6b312eb1af5c49c374ff","tid":1881022,"uid":323043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"平行時空（西貢），本身已經有兩個隔離營<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一，麥理浩夫人度假村<br />\n二，北潭涌保良局渡假營</span><br />\n黎緊，亦都會多一個<br />\n就係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西貢户外康樂中心</span><br />\n過去既一次遊行<br />\n有史以黎第一次<br />\n西貢一個平衡時空終於打破左<br />\n大家都知道西貢廢老藍絲最多<br />\n相比起 和理非 勇武 哨兵 更加少知有少<br />\n聽日，西貢居民大會，由三位議員舉辦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反對通知書已成功申請</span><br />\n唔排除 班綠色生物會腰斬<br />\n如果聽日，都係撤回唔到使用西貢户外康樂中心<br />\n香港人，我對你哋唔住，千祈唔好入嚟西貢<br />\n海 山 既活動 希望你哋暫停 <br />\n我哋唔想傳染比你地 <br />\n聽日，可能係最後一次為香港抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n一個黎自平行時空既手足 上<br />\n#FightForFreedomStandWithHongKong<br />\n#光復香港時代革命<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"f431d563dcd63d7ca4e1d89a9525d1a7a5b10b24","tid":1881022,"uid":323043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKhRLo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKhRLo8.png&h=f4a9a03d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"469b60dd2b0fcdcac6925a5e60a34bdd7f3e44a3","tid":1881022,"uid":323043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHsY9QX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHsY9QX.jpg&h=f8a8198b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"843bf282c4e7cd249996d0aa1ae610b4897b46f9","tid":1881022,"uid":323043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pPXFXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pPXFXK.jpg&h=e822856c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3602eec73d558569b0c05e262deac436705ae78","tid":1881022,"uid":281449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"如果我地聽日失敗咗，西貢人求下大家唔好再入嚟"}]}